Update:
I've checked the method to work normally with all models from torch/vision:

m.densenet121, m.densenet161, m.densenet169, m.densenet201,
m.resnet18, m.resnet34, m.resnet50, m.resnet101, m.resnet152,
m.squeezenet1_0, m.squeezenet1_1, m.alexnet,
m.vgg11, m.vgg11_bn, m.vgg13, m.vgg13_bn, m.vgg16, m.vgg16_bn, m.vgg19, m.vgg19_bn,

I've also performed minimal check for some models from

  • https://github.com/OpenNMT/OpenNMT-py
  • https://github.com/r9y9/deepvoice3_pytorch

body:
Update: 
I've checked the method to work normally with all models from torch/vision:
```
m.densenet121, m.densenet161, m.densenet169, m.densenet201,
m.resnet18, m.resnet34, m.resnet50, m.resnet101, m.resnet152,
m.squeezenet1_0, m.squeezenet1_1, m.alexnet,
m.vgg11, m.vgg11_bn, m.vgg13, m.vgg13_bn, m.vgg16, m.vgg16_bn, m.vgg19, m.vgg19_bn, 
```

I've also performed minimal check for some models from 

- https://github.com/OpenNMT/OpenNMT-py 
- https://github.com/r9y9/deepvoice3_pytorch
